The heart calms down in the flickering of flames.... \! The
party's health has been fully restored!

I apologize for the wait. My name is Hidarii. I will do my
best to assist everyone with unwavering determination.

My name is Migii. I swear upon the name of the Elysian
Knights to support everyone with all my might.

\SE[68]Um... I'm sorry, but I didn't really remember at all.
\SE[15]Which one was who again...
I apologize...! If I do this, I'm sure you'll understand...!

\SE[17]I suddenly understood...! My self-introduction skills
are too good...!!

\SE[2] How did the battle over there go? I hope there were
no casualties...

The situation was slightly unfavorable, but it ended with a
one- on-one duel between the Princess and the Chairman! \!I
suffered a little injury, but the Princess will be resting
in high spirits!

However, with Lord Cat's Flash Bullet, I managed to make the
situation ambiguous! It seems that I was successful in
disrupting their position over there!

\SE[72]But to safely return from facing the Chairman, that
Princess is quite impressive...

\SE[76]Well... this should be enough for an introduction.
\SE[3]From here on, we will split the team into two groups.

\SE[2]First, let's consider the balance... Allocate it to
'me' and 'Lunaroa' respectively.

\SE[52] My team will take on the Chairman. \SE[51] Lunaroa's
team will go after King Codaen... to defeat him. \SE[2]...
Does anyone have any objections so far?

\SE[50]... It seems fine. \!\SE[3]Due to the route's
circumstances, Cat will join me. Migii and Hidarii will go
with Lunaroa.

\SE[2]Laura, Vita are free slots, but... \SE[3]Do you have
any preferences?
\SE[50]I... I want to be useful to someone who seems...

\SE[60]No, you don't have to be so awkward... \SE[3]Join
Lunaroa's team. That way, even this pervert will feel
motivated.

\SE[15]I'm glad we're on the same team. \SE[15]Please
protect me properly, okay?
\SE[57]Hey, Vega...? Didn't you call me a pervert earlier?

\SE[2]No, I didn't say that. \!\SE[3]I wouldn't say
something like that in such a serious situation.

\SE[42]I wonder if that's true... \!\SE[43]I'm pretty sure
you said it for sure...

\SE[72]...So, Vita, I'll leave it to you over here.
\SE[7]Honestly, I can't rely on Cat, so I'm counting on you.
I'm counting on you.

\SE[1]I guess there's no other choice...! Leave everything
to me!

\SE[3]For the infiltration, I will use Auto Boat-kun, who
is now deceased, and his lover, Swishy-chan! \SE[3]Once we
go ahead, there's no turning back, so please be careful.

\SE[47] (We've been separated from our lovers... \SE[48]
We're such a tragic couple...)

...Ah, that's right. I was entrusted with a farewell gift of
encouragement from Princess Yurisine. She said, I hope you
can make good use of it, Laura!... apparently.
\SE[12]...Why are you calling me out by name!?
Laura received the Yuri Princess Medal! $
